---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
import ContactForm from './ContactForm.astro';
import Map from './Map.astro';
---

<section class="rounded-2xl py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-900 to-neutral-950">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:flex-row">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Entre em contato</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Preencha o formulário abaixo ou entre em contato diretamente pelos meus canais de comunicação.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mb-8">
          <a
            href="https://wa.me/5545998508634?text=Olá! Peguei seu contato no seu BLOG, tenho interesse em conversar contigo a respeito dos seus serviços."
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-white bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors px-6 py-3 rounded-lg"
          >
            <Icon name="mdi:whatsapp" class="w-5 h-5" />
            <span>Fale pelo WhatsApp</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <Icon name="mdi:map-marker" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" />
            <span>Cascavel - PR</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <Icon name="mdi:email" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" />
            <span>gustavolnomelini@gmail.com</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <Icon name="mdi:phone" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" />
            <span>(45) 99850-8634</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <ContactForm />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-16 h-[400px] rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
      <Map location="Cascavel, PR, Brasil" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 